Detailed Description

Structure for parameter definitions for content type properties.

Field Documentation

const CHAR* SyncMLCTParam::m_param_name
 

Specifies name of a supported parameter of a given content type property. Corresponds to the ParamName element in the SyncML Device Information DTD.
